@startuml Arquitetura_Simples_Startup_Collab
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    BorderColor #0D47A1
    BorderThickness 3
    FontSize 14
}
skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor #FFCCBC
    BorderColor #E65100
    BorderThickness 3
    FontSize 14
}

title Arquitetura da Aplicação - Startup Collab Platform\n\nCatólica SC - Engenharia de Software

' Componentes Principais
component [React Frontend\nVite + Tailwind] as Frontend
component [Express API\nNode.js] as Backend
database [PostgreSQL\nDatabase] as DB
component [Redis\nCache] as Redis

' Deploy
cloud [Vercel\nProduction] as Vercel
cloud [Koyeb\nProduction] as Koyeb

' Fluxo de Dados
Frontend --> Backend : REST API\n(HTTPS)
Backend --> DB : SQL Queries
Backend --> Redis : Cache\nRate Limiting

' Deploy
Vercel --> Frontend : Frontend Deploy
Koyeb --> Backend : Backend Deploy
Koyeb --> DB : Database Connection
Koyeb --> Redis : Cache Connection

note right of Frontend
  **Frontend:**
  - React 18+
  - Vite (Build)
  - React Router
  - Tailwind CSS
  - Zustand (State)
  
  **Páginas:**
  - Login/Register
