  - Profile
  - Matches
end note

note right of Backend
  **Backend:**
  - Node.js + Express
  - Clean Architecture
  - JWT Authentication
  - express-validator
  - Rate Limiting
  
  **Rotas:**
  - /api/users
  - /api/projects
  - /api/matches
  - /api/recommendations
end note

note left of DB
